### Get Item by ID
# Replace with actual UUID after creating an item
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/{{itemId}}

### Get books an item appears in
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/{{itemId}}/books

### Create an Item (with series and optional book associations)
POST {{baseUrl}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seriesId": "{{seriesId}}",
  "name": "Shardblade",
  "description": "A magical sword that can cut through anything except living flesh, which it kills instantly.",
  "image": "https://example.com/shardblade.jpg",
  "bookIds": ["{{bookId1}}", "{{bookId2}}"]
}

